Package de.targodan.usb.io.processing

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Handler
    Implementations of Handler handle commands calls and reports calling the appropriate methods on the registered CaseManager.
    Marshaller
    Implementations of Marshaller should marshall an arbitrary Object into an IRCMessage.
    Parser
    Implementations of Parser should parse and handle a message.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMarshaller  
    Command
    Command represents a command and its parameters.
    DefaultHandler
    DefaultHandler represents the default implementation of the Handler interface.
    DefaultParser
    DefaultParser is the default implementation of the Parser interface.
    HexchatMarshaller
    This implementation of Marshaller marshalls lines as formatted by the HexChat IRC client.
    IRCMessage
    IRCMessage represents an IRC message including the timestamp, sender, channel and content.
    mIRCMarshaller
    This implementation of Marshaller marshalls lines as formatted by the mIRC IRC client.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Command.Type
    Type represents a command type.
    ParseResult
    Represents the parsing result.
